headline: PACCAR (PCAR) Q3 2024 Earnings Call Transcript
summary: PACCAR earned a strong $972 million on revenues of $8.2 billion for an industry-leading after-tax return on revenue of 11.8%.  PACCAR Parts' third quarter revenues increased 5% to $1.66 billion and pre-tax profits were $407 million.  PACCAR Financial earned pre-tax income of $107 million in the third quarter.
